{"tid":1124700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昂山素姬：中國是緬甸好榜樣","createTime":"2019-04-25T07:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T07:58:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f2d5f21c4e01fc9a41f9538361137f162c6281","tid":1124700,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/04/25/2119118_fac3e8a4025249cf64a591c1790c8ca8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2F2119118_fac3e8a4025249cf64a591c1790c8ca8.jpg&h=7b9fd4bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸國務資政昂山素姬在北京出席一帶一路國際高峰論壇時表示，中國是緬甸一個榜樣，證明了有決心、有了努力與勤奮最後能夠得到什麼，世界上沒有任何一個國家在勤奮這點上能夠超越中國。<br />\n<br />\n昂山素姬表示，今次是帶着友誼而來，沒有相互信任和理解，就不會有真正的友誼與合作，希望在相互信任和理解的基礎之上建立合作和友誼的關係，而不是一種以影響力和權力為基礎的合作。<br />\n<br />\n她又感謝各國給予幫助，期待緬甸進步與發展，能為世界人民的福祉做出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2119118/昂山素姬%3A中國是緬甸好榜樣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2119118%2F%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%A7%AC%253A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E5%A5%BD%E6%A6%9C%E6%A8%A3&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=ff6ba1ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2119118/昂山素姬%3A中國是緬甸好榜樣</a>"},{"pid":"bad37c033823ddc84fd0c7498cb86dcb64792b6e","tid":1124700,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"政客全部信唔過<br />\n人有權力係會變"},{"pid":"b5f6055b246e2acdac662368d0e5e01dd6601a90","tid":1124700,"uid":190333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"叫軍方以中共搞鳩劉曉波一樣搞鳩你?"},{"pid":"225d0e7ab363652c7ae22f76849820c84e817ff1","tid":1124700,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨製造的第2個科學怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 